  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO ESTABLISH THE MISSISSIPPI TALENT EXCHANGE FOR ADVANCEMENT OF CAREERS AND HIGHER EDUCATION (TEACH) CREDIT ACT; TO PROVIDE A STATE INCOME TAX CREDIT FOR PRIVATE EMPLOYERS WHO LOAN QUALIFIED EMPLOYEES TO MISSISSIPPI COMMUNITY COLLEGES AS INSTRUCTORS IN HIGH-DEMAND CAREER AND TECHNICAL EDUCATION DISCIPLINES; TO PROVIDE FOR ADMINISTRATION, ELIGIBILITY, AND REPORTING REQUIREMENTS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
